<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/199601AKHRDSJTDQDCNHJBMDTCHMCSLBM> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A History of Motown";
  schema:description """
	Experience the soulful sounds of Motown in a mesmerizing concert starring the award-winning Krystle Dos Santos and her band! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get schooled on soul. A History of Motown takes you on a deep dive through the legends, chart‑topping hits, and unforgettable stories that shaped an era of music.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From humble beginnings in Detroit’s “Hitsville U.S.A.” to the global stage, this high-energy production brings the music, the moves, and the magic of Motown to life. Discover the stories behind the songs, the artists who broke barriers, and the sound that defined a generation. Following sold‑out shows and overwhelming audience response, <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">A History of Motown</span></span> is more than a concert. It’s a full‑on celebration. From the infectious grooves of The Supremes to the timeless brilliance of Stevie Wonder, Dos Santos brings Motown’s magic to life with unforgettable vocals, magnetic stage presence, and an electric, feel‑good atmosphere. 
""";
