<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/198801AQDPVRJTGKPPTMKNSVJNTHMCGMG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Glob";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Glob</span></span> is a fun, family event full of surprises, circus charm, and magical moments! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Two funny, sweet, and ageless clowns take the time to laugh, cry, and play; the time to exist. Through impressive balancing, contortion, diabolo, and hand-to-hand acts, this deeply human and comical work amazes children and gives adults a break from the frantic pace of everyday life. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Without a single word, two lovable characters tumble, glide and soar through the unknown. Join them as they discover a world that is tender, magical and wonderfully absurd. They’ll make you laugh, gasp and cheer – all while tugging at your heart. For anyone who needs the world to slow down just a little, Glob is a wordless journey where emotion speaks louder than words. Inspired by silent cinema and its essential icons like Charlie Chaplin, Buster Keaton, and Laurel and Hardy, Glob is a clown show magnificently sprinkled with poetry and light. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Perfect for all ages, it will delight and enchant audiences, young and old. Don’t miss this unforgettable ride! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Glob was created by Les Foutoukours, one of the most popular theatre companies in Quebec, which has staged 22 production in their 27 years of existence. Les Foutoukours shows have travelled all over the world, won awards, and, above all, the hearts of more than 500,000 spectators.  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“A little imagination and innocence are enough to rise above everyday troubles and marvel at everything!”</span> - La Provence <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“The show is particularly beautiful, unique and enchanting.”</span> - Ici Radio-Canada 
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-11-30T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/files/e32cd02d-7e88-4e49-8acd-b002b5b25d84.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/sidwilliams/location/201AGBHDRLQHNHPHKKMPKLGPMDRDTDMVL>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/sidwilliams/organization/sid-williams-theatre-society>;
  schema:url <https://www.sidwilliamstheatre.com/events/glob/>;
  schema:offers _:c92eb91bdcdc4d86a3b73bc5ae6539c21386;
  schema:keywords "Cirque";
  schema:duration "PT65M";
  schema:endDate "2026-11-30T20:05:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

