<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/183801AGRPKBNGPJRTMCMMJKMGMVVJBLR> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Groove 2026";
  schema:description """
	Pantuso Dance proudly presents Groove 2026! Step into an evening where movement becomes music and the stage comes alive with creativity, spirit, and heart. Groove 2026 is a celebration of dance in all its forms; an invitation to witness the dedication, artistry, and passion of our incredible performers.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From the rhythmic brilliance of tap to the timeless grace of ballet, the vibrant energy of hip hop to the bold style of jazz, and from the emotional depth of contemporary to the theatrical sparkle of musical theatre, this performance weaves together a rich tapestry of movement and expression. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Each piece reflects countless hours of practice, imagination, and collaboration. Through every leap, turn, and rhythm-filled step, our dancers share their love of dance and the joy of performing. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We hope you enjoy this evening of artistry, community, and celebration as our dancers take the stage to share the work they have poured their hearts into. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Feel the rhythm. <span><br/></span>Share the energy. <span><br/></span>Celebrate the joy of dance. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Passion. Dedication. Performance. <span><br/></span>
""";
