  schema:priceCurrency "CAD" .

<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/193001AJHPNSNHDGSNDHLCNJVJSCTKVGN> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "MOONDANCE: The Van Morrison Songbook";
  schema:description """
	Mystic Celtic Soul singer and songwriter, Van Morrison has placed his indelible stamp upon Western Music culture with a career spanning over half a century! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>As the voice of “Van the Man” Bruce Coughlan (ISSA International Singer Songwriter Award Top Male Vocalist 2024) brings one of his major influences to life with an uncanny ability to make you shut your eyes and think the great Van is in the room. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The band with Bruce includes some of the top musicians on Canada’s West Coast including Tiller’s Folly bandmate Laurence Knight, Bass and Vocals, Greg Stuart Drums and Vocals, Lee Warden Keys Guitar Vocals, Karen Graves, saxes flute and vocals, and Geeta Das Trumpet. These musicians have performed with Michael Buble, Colin James, Adele, Ian Tyson, Long John Baldry, Shari Ulrich, Jim Byrnes, Mike Reno, Taj Mahal, Roy Forbes, Corb Lund etc etc. Drummer Chris is a six time “Maple Blues Drummer of the Year” nominee.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See you in September!
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-09-25T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/files/4a3b37dd-a721-4116-a191-e07fc70778af.jpg>;
