<http://www.spektrix.com/sidwilliams/event/199801AQBNMSBJVJBHVHTDJPHVRRQTKCN> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Oh Pray Tell";
  schema:description """
	Oh Pray Tell is a transdisciplinary music group – three-part harmonies grounded in banjo and stomp-clap-cajon rhythms carry poetry, stories and spoken word. Oh Pray Tell offers up an original, soulful sound influenced by gospel, rhythm & blues, roots music and folk storytelling. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Their music is known for its emotional depth, themes of belonging and identity, and community-centered performances. Based in British Columbia, Turtle Island, Oh Pray Tell tours across rural and urban spaces, bringing messages of hope, resilience, and connection to audiences far and wide. 
""";
