	Show number TEN, UNLOCKED! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For one night only, they're opening the vault and bringing back your all-time favourite Valley Girls numbers; the ones that shook the stage & left you wanting more! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The crowd favourites. <span><br/></span>The iconic moments. <span><br/></span>The routines that hit hard then…and hit even harder now! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From heels to hype, sexy to savage, this is a full-throttle celebration of every era that built Valley Girls Dance. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is The VG Vault; unlocked, reimagined, and better than ever. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come support local dancers and join VGD for a night of jaw dropping performances!  (Audience 17+)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is your chance to relive it, re-love it, and reignite the obsession! <span><br/></span>
